{"article_id":"8l41u2MtPe6yyACw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"There are growing warnings on Capitol Hill","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that the nation could be rolling toward an end-of-the-year fiscal train wreck .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"`` The looming tax hike will be absolutely devastating , ''","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , said .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"`` You can call this a fiscal cliff .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"You can call it 'Taxmageddon '","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"as others have done .","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"Whatever you call it ,","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"it will be a disaster for the middle class , ''","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch , R-Utah , added .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"And Sen. Ben Nelson , D-Neb. , said :","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"`` It 's a tsunami ;","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"there 's no question about it ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and it 's coming . ''","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"What 's coming ?","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"The Bush-era tax cuts expire along with the payroll tax break ;","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"the nation 's borrowing authority bumps against its limit ;","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"and huge mandatory spending cuts","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"- half targeting defense -","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"are set to kick in .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"All this could trigger another recession ,","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"but Congress is not likely to do much about it until after November 's election .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"Last week , the nonpartisan Congressional Budget Office also weighed in :","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Unless Congress acts to change current law ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"it said ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"spending cuts and tax increases could shrivel next year 's growth to a mere one-half of 1 percent ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"which would probably be seen as a recession .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Earlier this month , Speaker John Boehner , R-Ohio , announced","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"that the House will vote to extend all of the Bush-era tax breaks .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"`` Any sudden tax hike would hurt our economy ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"so this fall , before the election , the House of Representatives will vote","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to stop the largest tax increase in American history , ''","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"It 's quite likely such a bill would pass , but only in the House .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Republicans could then use that vote on the campaign trail","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"to accuse House Democrats","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"who might oppose the measure","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"of wanting to raise everyone 's taxes .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"But Democratic leaders insist","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"tax breaks for the very wealthy should not be extended .","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"Senate Majority leader Harry Reid , D-Nev. , responded last week to the GOP colleagues","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"who 'd written","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"demanding","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"that the Senate renew all the expiring cuts .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"`` I say to the 41 Republicans and Sen. Hatch","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"who sent me this letter ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"move on revenues ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"we could have had a deal a long time ago , ''","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"`` The president said that","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"when we got together at the White House last Wednesday . ''","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Reid has also made it clear","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"he will not back GOP efforts","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to spare the Pentagon from some $ 50 billion in automatic spending cuts next year","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"in what 's known as `` the sequester . ''","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"The threat of such cuts was meant to spur Congress into agreeing on a 10-year deficit reduction deal ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"but the deal never came together .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Reid says","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Congress must now face the consequences .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"`` I do n't like sequester .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"... It was a hard pill","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"to swallow ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"but it was the right thing","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"to do , ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"`` If we 're going to ever reduce the staggering deficits ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"we 're going to have to make some hard decisions . ''","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"That sets up a fight over the sequester with defense hawks","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"led by Sen. John McCain of Arizona , the top Republican on the Senate Armed Services Committee .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"`` I just ca n't imagine it going through","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"because of what","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"[ Defense ] Secretary [ Leon ] Panetta describes as a devastating impact on our ability","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to defend this nation , ''","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"`` That 's our country 's first priority . ''","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Not all Republicans side with McCain .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Alaska Sen. Lisa Murkowski says","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"the sequester is a hammer","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"meant to move Congress to come up with deficit reduction","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"- for which she wo n't rule out higher tax revenues .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"`` We 've got a responsibility","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"to figure this out , ''","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"`` I 'm not going to suggest","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that we just pull the plug","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and say","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that never happened . ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Meanwhile , some Republicans and Democrats in the Senate have begun private talks about ways","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"to prevent falling off a fiscal cliff at year 's end .","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"One of them , Colorado Democrat Michael Bennet , says","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"everything depends on who wins in November .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"`` Not to mix a metaphor ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"but these are huge tectonic plates","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that are going to shift after this election ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"when it 's not just the tax cuts expiring , but the sequester and the debt ceiling and all the rest , ''","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"`` And I think","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"it 's very unlikely that anything 's going to be done before the election . ''","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Lobbyist Trent Lott , a former Mississippi senator and Republican majority leader , says","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"he 's seen many other lame-duck sessions after big elections ,","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"but none like the one","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"coming up .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"`` If everything stays pretty much status quo ,","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"they might do some things in a lame-duck session ,","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"if it 's like ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"you know ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"the House stays Republican ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"the Senate stays Democrat","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and Obama stays in , ''","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"`` Any other mixture or any other result , it 'll probably all be pushed until next year . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":221,"left":150,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left